armenians demands over the annexation issue a sympathy strike 
began on july 4 in yerevan but speakers at a weekend rally urged 
people to return to work in expectation of the presidium meeting 
tensions caused by the territorial dispute also led to ethnic 
rioting in the azerbaijani city of sumgait on feb 28 officials 
said 32 people 26 of them armenians were killed 
