<TEXT>
rick james the selfprofessed king of 
punkfunk rock calls his latest album wonderful with good 
reason 
thats the way i feel since ive been off motown said 
james referring to the legendary recording label which released 
the string of singles you and i super freak i 
coldblooded that catapulted james to superstardom during the 
past 10 years 
