<TEXT>
the sanders have swapped rowdy alaskan 
bars for more gentle settings to sing their songs of love 
after fighting off grizzly bears and gold thieves in the land of 
the midnight sun the brothersister duo came to nashville with 
their closeknit vocals and launched a country music recording 
career 
vicki sanders 31 and dale 33 spent the past 10 years singing 
in alaska at night and often mining for gold by day with their 
father a retired geology teacher 
it was very rewarding dale sanders said it was nice 
being able to make people smile all the time 
vicki sanders gave a sample of their experiences 
we played in barrow in the far northern part we were hired 
with 13 colombians who never went to sleep they partied nonstop 
there were two buckets for the bathroom and a shower stall that 
said girls mondaywednesdayfriday and boys tuesdaythursday 
in seward a girl was beating a guy up she picked up a 
chair and threw it at him he ran into the bathroom and hid he 
stepped out and she sucker punched him 
a guy threatened to tie his wife to a tree so she shot him 
nine times with a 22 at their cabin she got on a snow machine and 
went for help 
the darkness and remoteness of alaska seemed to affect the 
residents the sanders said 
in all those remote places where its dark people have a 
tendency to get wild and kick up their heels vicki said it 
gets depressing 
you get a different breed of people said dale those who 
dont like society go to those type places its kind of the end of 
the road 
the two also had to contend with bears while mining along the 
alaskacanada border 
we were pretty heavily armed at the mine because they would 
surprise you or you would surprise them dale said in an 
interview youd be in a bind without a weapon they destroyed 
our camp a couple of times one time they walked through a 
campertrailer by going in one end and tearing out the whole wall 
and destroying the inside they pushed a refrigerator through the 
wall and made another hole to go out 
they mined from 1973 until the mid1980s always on the lookout 
for thieves 
one guy took a chain saw and stole the floor out of a cabin 
dale said 
the two both born and raised in alaska compared the mining 
business to the entertainment field 
some years were good and some were not very good at all 
