doesnt resemble theirs in any way only that we are brother and 
sister we do have kind of a folk influence which they did also 
our music is kind of on the sweet side but ours is not as 
sweet as theirs ours is more country dale said weve got a 
new sound with a different approach we dont sound like anyone 
else our music is easy to listen to positive straight ahead 
the sanders are the latest in a variety of family acts in 
country music joining larry gatlin and the gatlin brothers the 
judds mother and daughter the forester sisters the whites 
father and daughters and others 
the blend you get when you put family together is going to be 
closer than if you are not related said vicki who has two other 
brothers 
and you make more concessions when working with family on the 
road you have disagreements but you forgive your brother or 
sister its harder to forgive someone not related 
said dale a lot of families grow up singing and just fall 
into it 
