until dec 31 1995 to buy gtes remaining 199 percent interest 
in us sprint at book value of dec 31 1988 or at book value at 
the time of the transaction whichever is higher 
otherwise gte would have the option of requiring united 
telecommunications to buy its remaining interest at any time 
between dec 31 1991 and dec 31 1995 at the book value 
prevailing at the time of the transaction 
